:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>Welcome to <strong>NxCut</strong> — your all-in-one salon management system. Whether you&#x27;re booking an appointment, collecting payment, managing your team, or checking how your business is doing, everything you need is right here.</p>\n<p>This guide walks you through every part of NxCut in plain, simple language. No technical experience needed.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"what-can-nxcut-do-for-you\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#what-can-nxcut-do-for-you\" class=\"peer\">What can NxCut do for you?</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 @container\"><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/dashboard\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Dashboard</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">See how your business is doing at a glance — revenue, appointments, and top performers.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/calendar\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Calendar &amp; Bookings</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Book, reschedule, and manage appointments for your whole team in one view.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/checkout\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Checkout</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Collect payment, apply discounts, add tips, and split bills — all in a few clicks.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/sales\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Sales Hub</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">View your full sales history — payments, memberships, vouchers, tips, and more.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/catalog\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Catalog &amp; Inventory</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Set up your services, products, membership packages, and gift vouchers.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/clients\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Clients</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Keep a full record of every client — their visits, memberships, and voucher balances.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/team\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Team Management</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Add staff, set their working hours, and control what they can access.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/commission\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Commission</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Automatically calculate how much each team member earns and generate salary slips.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/reporting\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Reporting</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Dig into your numbers — sales trends, payment breakdowns, tips, and more.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/settings\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Settings</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Set up your locations, business hours, payment options, and access rules.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a><a data-card=\"true\" class=\"block rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-4 text-fd-card-foreground transition-colors @max-lg:col-span-full hover:bg-fd-accent/80\" href=\"/docs/website\"><h3 class=\"not-prose mb-1 text-sm font-medium\">Website &amp; Booking Page</h3><p class=\"my-0! text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\">Manage your public booking page and let clients book appointments online.</p><div class=\"text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"></div></a></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"finding-your-way-around\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#finding-your-way-around\" class=\"peer\">Finding your way around</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>When you log in, you&#x27;ll see a menu on the left side of the screen. Each item takes you to a different part of NxCut.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Section</th><th>What it&#x27;s for</th><th>Who can see it</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/dashboard\">Dashboard</a></td><td>Business overview and key numbers</td><td>Admins only</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/calendar\">Calendar</a></td><td>Appointments and bookings</td><td>All staff</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/sales\">Sales</a></td><td>Sales history and transactions</td><td>All staff</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/clients\">Clients</a></td><td>Client directory and profiles</td><td>All staff</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/catalog\">Catalog</a></td><td>Services, products, and packages</td><td>All staff</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/team\">Team</a></td><td>Staff profiles and schedules</td><td>All staff</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/commission\">Commission</a></td><td>Earnings and salary slips</td><td>Admins only</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/reporting\">Reports</a></td><td>Financial reports and analytics</td><td>Admins only</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/docs/settings\">Settings</a></td><td>Business configuration</td><td>Admins only</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p><strong>Admin vs. Staff</strong> — Admin users can access everything. Regular staff only see what they need for their daily work: Calendar, Sales, Clients, Catalog, and Team.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-1\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/dashboard\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Dashboard</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A real-time overview of your salon&#x27;s performance — revenue, appointments, and top staff</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" view